# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# QuickBike Backend — Environment Configuration
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Copy this file to .env and fill in real values.
# NEVER commit .env to version control.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Core ──
NODE_ENV=development
PORT=3000

# ── Database (MongoDB) ──
DB_CONNECT=mongodb+srv://user:pass@cluster.mongodb.net/quickbike
DB_MAX_POOL=10
DB_MIN_POOL=2

# ── Redis (optional in dev, required in prod) ──
REDIS_URL=redis://127.0.0.1:6379

# ── JWT — Users ──
JWT_SECRET=change-me-to-a-64-char-random-string-user
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=15m
JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=change-me-to-a-64-char-random-string-refresh
JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRES_IN=7d

# ── JWT — Admin (separate secret, shorter expiry) ──
ADMIN_JWT_SECRET=change-me-to-a-64-char-random-string-admin
ADMIN_JWT_EXPIRES_IN=8h

# ── Google Maps ──
GOOGLE_MAPS_API=your-google-maps-api-key

# ── Razorpay ──
RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=rzp_test_xxxxxxxxxxxx
RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
RAZORPAY_WEBHOOK_SECRET=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# ── Cloudinary ──
CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=your-cloud-name
CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=your-api-key
CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=your-api-secret

# ── SMS (MSG91 / Twilio) ──
MSG91_AUTH_KEY=your-msg91-auth-key
MSG91_TEMPLATE_ID=your-template-id

# ── Email (SendGrid) ──
SENDGRID_API_KEY=SG.xxxxxxxxxxxx
SENDGRID_FROM_EMAIL=noreply@quickbike.in

# ── Push Notifications (FCM) ──
FCM_SERVER_KEY=your-fcm-server-key

# ── CORS (comma-separated origins) ──
CORS_ORIGINS=http://localhost:5173,http://localhost:5174

# ── Rate Limiting ──
RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_MS=900000
RATE_LIMIT_MAX=100

# ── Error Tracking ──
SENTRY_DSN=
